thread.title: Report shows North Korea testing nuclear reactor

title: Report shows North Korea testing nuclear reactor
text:
Report shows North Korea testing nuclear reactor Friday, March 16, 2018 - 01:15 
South Korean officials are beginning preparations for a summit next month with North Korea, as a report shows the North had probably begun testing a nuclear reactor as recently as late February.
